Thanks for waiting for the latest update! Here’s what we’ve fixed:

- Showing tasks you’ve made an offer on in ‘Offers Made’ area 
- Updating the location when posting a task
- When trying to ‘continue’ within the cleaning post a task form

 If you spot or encounter any issues, please let us know asap at support@airtasker.com or from the Help menu in the app so we can squash them right away!

Thanks for waiting for the latest update! 

- Our new & improved Payment History allows you to view all earned and outgoing transactions on Airtasker. You can also download a CSV report. Go to  "More" > "Payment History".
- *Brand New*  Task receipt . See a  financial breakdown of your completed tasks. View in task screen.
- Fix crashes when selecting locations
- Fix missing comment text & bid offer when reviewing offers

 If you spot or encounter any issues, please let us know asap at support@airtasker.com or from the Help menu in the app so we can squash them right away!

Thanks for waiting for the latest update! 

Improvements
- Added some polish to make the new cancellation flow look even spiffier.

Fixes
- Fix review counts when there are no reviews.
- Fix crashes that were affecting some people with the new seperate Job Poster and Airtasker Worker reviews.
- Fix occasional crash when viewing tasks with offers.

 If you spot or encounter any issues, please let us know asap at support@airtasker.com or from the Help menu in the app so we can squash them right away!

We've just released an update LIKE A BOSS.

New
- To improve the integrity of reviews. When a review is left it is hidden until the other party also leaves a review, or the seven day review window has expired.

Improvements
- Credit card expiry dates now have a full 4 digits for years.
- No option to request or release funds for tasks with a cancellation request.

Fixes
- Stop crashes when declining task cancellation requests.
- Fix occasional crash in background.

If you spot or encounter any issues, please let us know ASAP at support@airtasker.com or from the Help menu in the app so we can squash them LIKE A BOSS.

If you spot or encounter any issues, please let us know ASAP at support@airtasker.com or from the Help menu in the app so we can squash them LIKE A BOSS.

New 
Help screen within More Options tab now includes:
- Customer support: connects members with company experts who can answer any queries or concerns.
- Terms and conditions: outlines the rules members must agree to in order to use Airtasker.
- Insurance: provides full details of the public liability policy, its coverage and exclusions including excess details.
- Privacy policy: describes how Airtasker handles your personal information, and sets out the rights and obligation that both you and Airtasker have in relation to your personal information.

- Those lovely referral coupon codes are now right where you need them when accepting an offer.
- Your ID Badges are also now visible for all the world to see (in your profile).
- And you can now find where you’re going with directions through maps (Apple and otherwise!).
- And to top it off we squashed some pesky bugs.

If you come across any issues, please let us know ASAP at support@airtasker.com or through the Help menu inside the app - we’ll give you a shout-out next release!

- So there was a weird error message that sometimes appeared when editing the billing address or payment methods. It’s dead Jim.
- Remember the last time you tapped a link to go to your favourite app (i.e. us ;D), and it crashed? That’s not a thing (anymore). Tap away! Yay!
- We also patched a bunch of other visibility issues in and around the profile area. See if you can spot them! :)

Remember, if you come across any issues, please let us know ASAP at support@airtasker.com or through the Help menu inside the app - we’ll give you a shout-out next release!

- Sending messages when looking at a task wasn’t always possible on iOS 11. Now that it’s fixed, it’s time to message ‘til your heart’s content! Thanks to everyone who reported it, this fix is for you.
- Once upon a time, declining a cancellation crashed the app. Now it doesn't. 
- So if (for some crazy reason) you tried to post a task without a budget, you’d get an error with no message that just said "OK". It's not "OK". That’s why we added a message.

If you come across any issues, get in touch ASAP at support@airtasker.com or through the Help menu inside the app - we'll give you a shout-out next release!

Hi there! So we hit a bit of a road-bump recently - it turns out the app was repeatedly crashing for a few users and we're going to have to roll the app back by a couple of versions.

Although we tried (and tried and tried and tried!) to fix the problem without rolling back, it turns out we have no other choice. We know that you may rely on Airtasker and nothing is more frustrating than when it doesn't work. That's why our main focus is making sure that it works reliably for you. 

Unfortunately, this also means that some of our latest features (like bonuses and a few other little fixes) won't be available for a little while. We'll be working to bring these back to you ASAP, but it may take a few months.

We really appreciate your patience. It turns out that sometimes you have to take 2 steps back to take 3 steps forward!

We'd also like to send out a huge thanks to everyone that helped out with identifying the problem - you're the best!
